            <p>We collect and process Client Data to provide and improve our services, customize AI Tools, and generate analytics.</p>
            <h3>6.2 Data Ownership</h3>
            <p><strong>You retain ownership</strong> of all Client Data. We claim no ownership rights to your client contacts, listing data, or business records.</p>
            <h3>6.3 Data Security</h3>
            <p>We implement industry-standard security measures including encryption in transit (TLS 1.3) and at rest (AES-256).</p>
            <h3>6.5 Mortgage Document Security</h3>
            <p>For clients using DealCheck™, documents are encrypted, stored in Canadian data centers, and automatically purged after 90 days.</p>
          </div>

          <div id="ip">
            <h2>7. INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY</h2>
            <p>We retain all rights to our AI Tools, algorithms, and trademarks. You retain all rights to your brand name, content, and data. Content generated by our AI Tools using your brand voice is licensed to you for unlimited commercial use.</p>
          </div>

          <div id="performance">
