            <p>We target 99% uptime for our AI Tools. Support response times vary by priority, ranging from 4 hours for critical issues to 5 business days for low priority requests.</p>
            <p><strong>Performance Expectations:</strong> While we strive for optimal results, we do not guarantee specific numbers of leads, conversions, or revenue amounts. AI performance depends on market conditions and factors outside our control.</p>
          </div>

          <div id="termination">
            <h2>9. TERM AND TERMINATION</h2>
            <p>This agreement begins upon execution of your Service Agreement. You may terminate Partnership Services with 30 days written notice. Implementation fees are non-refundable unless specified otherwise.</p>
          </div>

