            <p>You may not use our services to violate laws, distribute spam, or infringe on third-party rights. AI-generated content must not make false claims or violate real estate advertising regulations.</p>
          </div>

          <div id="third-party">
            <h2>14. THIRD-PARTY SERVICES</h2>
            <p>Our services may integrate with third-party platforms. You are responsible for maintaining accounts and complying with their terms. We are not liable for third-party service outages.</p>
          </div>

          <div id="modifications">
            <h2>15. MODIFICATIONS TO TERMS</h2>
            <p>We reserve the right to modify these Terms. Changes become effective 30 days after notice for existing clients.</p>
          </div>

          <div id="disputes">
