            <p>BY SIGNING A SERVICE AGREEMENT, CLICKING "I ACCEPT," OR USING OUR SERVICES, YOU ACKNOWLEDGE THAT:</p>
            <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-2 font-sans text-sm text-[#2c2c2c]/80">
              <li>You have read and understood these Terms</li>
              <li>You agree to be bound by these Terms</li>
              <li>You have authority to enter this agreement</li>
